                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#92v"/>
                           <desc>Paraphrasis of an oration for sunday</desc>
                           <note>The note begins as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">ዘበሰማያት፡ 
                                    <sic>አበነ፡</sic>
                                  ዘበምድር፡ ኣዲ፡ ግብተ፡ እንበለ፡ 
                                    <sic>ታጉንዲ፡</sic>
                                  
                              ዘታብእል፡ ወዘታነዲ።</q>, and terminates as follows: <q xml:lang="gez">
                                    <sic>እግዚአ፡</sic>
                                  ሃበነ፡ መክፈልተ፡ ፀጋ፡ ዘይሴኒ፡ 
                                    <sic>ለነፍሰ፡</sic>
                                  ወስጋ።</q>.</note>
                        </item>
                      
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#1r"/>
                           <desc type="Unclear">Unidentified note in Arabic</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="ar">ونالت النصرانية اليهود عاى شي وفا ... اليهود لست اليهود على شي فصد ... قالوا دخلوا النار</q>
                           <note>The note is written on two lines and is mostly erased.</note>
                        </item>
                    
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc>The shelfmark of the Vatican Library <q xml:lang="la">Vat. | 34 | Aethiop.</q> is written on the cover, together with the coat of arms of 
